data.description: Escape the ordinary with this enchanting ranch-style log home set on a sprawling 12 acre estate. A blend of rustic charm and modern comfort, this 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom residence boasts a finished basement with a separate entrance, making it a versatile space for guests or a potential rental unit. Upon entering, you're welcomed by the warmth of the log interior, highlighting the cozy living room and a spacious kitchen with an inviting island perfect for both everyday meals and entertaining. The main floor also features three bedrooms, each providing a comfortable retreat after a day spent enjoying the surrounding natural beauty. Descend into the finished basement, where a fully equipped kitchen,  living room,  bedroom and bathroom await. The separate entrance adds convenience and flexibility, making this space ideal for guests, extended family, or as an income-generating rental. The main house has a delightful sunroom, featuring glass windows that bathe the space in natural light and a hot tub, creating a perfect spot to unwind in any season. For the equestrian enthusiast, the property includes a barn with stalls for horses and a workshop for your projects and hobbies. Two outbuildings provide ample storage space, ensuring that you have room for all your equipment and tools. Embrace the tranquility of this picturesque setting, where the expansive grounds offer endless possibilities for outdoor activities and enjoyment. Whether you're strolling through the well-maintained grounds or exploring the nearby trails, this property is a nature lover's dream. Don't miss the chance to make this unique log home yours. Schedule a showing today and experience the perfect fusion of comfort, charm, and country living.
